The Fruit Of Hard Work
Ritu studied in the ninth class. One day the teacher gave all the students a project on a particular subject which was to be completed only in 3 days
All the chidren including Rita's friends were upset as to how they would complete the project in such a short period.Ritu worked very hard and 
completed the project in the given time. When she reached the school the 3rd day most of her classmates including her friends made excuses for not
having completed the project.The teacher was very happy with Ritu as she was the only one to complete the project.She got full marks in the project.
 

 Moral: Hard Work produces fruits of pleasure